{
  "texts": [
    "As described earlier, we pre-train the speech encoder and the learnable parameters in the speech synthesizer to perform a speech-to-speech auto-encoding task.",
    "We use multiple loss terms for the training.",
    "The modified multi-scale spectral (MSS) loss is inspired by ref.",
    "53 and is defined as",
    "with L(x, y) = ‖x -y‖ 1 + ‖ ‖ log xlog y ‖ ‖ 1"
  ]
}